# 目录结构强制规范

## PRD路径

**路径**: `docs/00_product/requirements/{REQ-ID}/{REQ-ID}.md`

## 测试用例CSV路径

**路径**: `docs/00_product/requirements/{REQ-ID}/{REQ-ID}-test-cases.csv`

## API契约路径

**路径**: `docs/01_guideline/api-contracts/{REQ-ID}/{REQ-ID}-api.yaml`

## 测试文件路径

- **单元测试**: `backend/tests/unit/test_{module}.py`
- **集成测试**: `backend/tests/integration/test_{feature}.py`
- **E2E测试**: `e2e/tests/{feature}.spec.ts`
- **回归测试**: `backend/tests/regression/test_{bug_id}.py`, `e2e/tests/regression/test-{bug_id}.spec.ts`

